## Next Steps

<steps>
  <step title="Install Zolto">

```bash
npm install -g zolto
zolto new my-docs
```

  </step>
  <step title="Open the editor">

```bash
cd my-docs
zolto dev
```

Navigate to `http://localhost:3000`.

  </step>
  <step title="Write your first document">
  Create a new file from the sidebar or press `Ctrl+N`. Start with a heading
  and a `<tip>` callout.
  </step>
  <step title="Export">
  Press `Ctrl+E` or use File → Export. Choose HTML, PDF, or Markdown.
  </step>
</steps>
